  <font face="Arial">
   circles the 
	dominant hand in an "A" hand shape underneath the non-dominant "flat" palm.
   <br/>
  </font>
  <br/>
  <img border="0" src="../../gifs/b/basement.gif" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto" width="480"/>
  <font face="Arial">
